License: UNKNOWN
Description: # CronMon
        
        ## Usage
        
        ```
        your-task.sh arguments | cronmon --name your-task --location ~/cronmon
        cronman --command "your-task.sh arguments" --name your-task --location ~/cronmon
        cronmon --command "script.sh" --location ~/cronmon --on-fail "fail-script.sh"
        ```
        
